Hi Bruce.  The reason I asked about the techs is, my normal guys are David & Patrick, and 
a woman whose name I&#39;ve never been told.  They come through on the MiniBox or manual 
radio sweep.  It seems I have a different tech group (five people) when I work with more 
traditional EVP methods, which I discovered nearly three years ago.   

I thought it interesting to have someone named Arthur come through via EVPM, as the 
name is new to me.  I&#39;ve long suspected that perhaps different groups assist with different 
technologies.  For instance, I have one team that seems to be unique to my work with light 
(phototransistor modified recorder and battery operated plasma globe combo.)

I&#39;m not sure what you mean by &quot;come up with the answer, backed up by a file.&quot;  

Margaret

